    "This involves adherence to existing regulations and proactive participation in the formulation of new ones that promote sustainability.",
    "-Innovation, Mindset, and Way of Working: this aspect focuses on instilling a culture of innovation, environmental consciousness, and adaptive working practices within the organization.",
    "It recognizes that true sustainability goes beyond compliance, requiring a mindset shift and a commitment to continuous improvement.",
